1.10	Lord_John_and_the_Haunted_Soldier_(novella)	Lord John and the Haunted Soldier	Lord John and the Haunted Soldier was written by Diana Gabaldon. It was initially published in Germany, but made its English language debut in the Lord John and the Hand of Devils collection. Historically taking place during the Seven Years War, non-fictional historic events and characters frequently make appearances throughout the Lord John series of novels and novellas. Fictional characters from several of Gabaldon's other novels also appear, or are referenced and non critical plot lines concerning events in the Outlander series may overlap.	
